{
  "stem": "21786.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And if we would get the order to go right, that would be the call for the uprising.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "After standing there for 20 minutes, we got the order-- turn left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we went with a tremendous speed through the sauna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "No, they usually cut your hair, and they shaved you all over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Nothing, nothing of that-- just quickly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They threw at us various types of this striped clothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the size, we had to change everything ourselves, among ourselves, for you got-- I mean, the trousers which were up until here, the guy who was too tall-- tall got the small.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But we managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they took us to this train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we entered the train-- we were 40 only in one wagon, 40 persons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I mean, prisoner was never a person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they were two soldiers in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And there was, I mean, a big kind of barrel with water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And there was a big drum for human facilities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And there was, I mean, some kind of a chemical to put into this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And there was whistling and yelling and God knows what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the train pulled out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we simply just looked, and the train was going into a turn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We looked out, and there was written [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we were out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were trying to get out of these soldiers-- where are we going?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is it all about?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were scared to talk, for they were given, I mean, all kinds of instructions, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't touch us, didn't hear, didn't say one word.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they slowly, realizing that we talk German, if necessary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they started to talk to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were scared to-- to even to permit us to take our excreta out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did it themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
